articles.title: Asia-Pacific markets set for mixed open as AI sell-off on Wall Street continues - CNBC
articles.description: Markets in Australia started the day higher, while markets in Japan and South Korea fell.
articles.content:
Asia-Pacific market fell across the board Tuesday, tracking Wall Street declines as investors continued to rotate out of the artificial intelligence trade in the U.S.
